==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Equally
<hw>E"qual*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In an equal manner or degree in
equal shares or proportion; with equal and impartial justice; without
difference; alike; evenly; justly; <as>as, <ex>equally</ex> taxed,
furnished, etc.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Equalness</ent>⟦br⟧
